        "id": "claim-main",
        "statement": "A viable beyond-braneworld extension strategy for rQFC must reproduce the braneworld benchmark, remain consistent with the Theta -> 0 improved-energy-condition limit, and accommodate the JT-gravity / d>2 tests without invoking braneworld holography as an unexplained black box.",
